%                              (EDIT continued)+

+  Once located the manual can be selected for editing or the manual can
   deleted from the library.

   Deleting the manual is done by placing a 'D' in front of the Manual I
   field and pressing enter.  The user is then asked to confirm the requ
   to delete the manual.  To confirm the request press enter or press th
   key to cancel the request.



   You terminate edit by using the END command.

   If you are editing detail data, END will take you back to the selecti
   screen.

   If you are displaying the selection screen, END will take you back to
   primary option menu.

)INIT
   &ZCONT = SLSS2000
   &ZUP   = SLSST000
)END
